<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Birthday Adventure</title>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.2/gsap.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #87CEFA, #fefefe);
            text-align: center;
        }
        #scene {
            position: relative;
            width: 100vw;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .item {
            position: absolute;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        #cake {
            width: 150px;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        }
        #balloons {
            width: 100px;
            top: 80%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }
        #giftBox {
            width: 120px;
            top: 90%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            display: none;
        }
        #message {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            font-size: 2em;
            color: #ff4081;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="scene">
        <img id="cake" class="item" src="https://i.imgur.com/A6p1YyR.png" alt="Birthday Cake">
        <img id="balloons" class="item" src="https://i.imgur.com/6K4ZJfJ.png" alt="Balloons">
        <img id="giftBox" class="item" src="https://i.imgur.com/X9YxuQ6.png" alt="Gift Box">
        <div id="message">Happy Birthday! ðŸŽ‰</div>
    </div>
    <script>
        gsap.to("#cake", { y: -150, duration: 2, repeat: -1, yoyo: true });
        document.getElementById("cake").addEventListener("click", function() {
            gsap.to("#cake", { scale: 0, duration: 1 });
            gsap.to("#balloons", { y: -600, duration: 3, onComplete: function() {
                document.getElementById("giftBox").style.display = "block";
            }});
        });
        document.getElementById("giftBox").addEventListener("click", function() {
            gsap.to("#giftBox", { scale: 0, duration: 1 });
            document.getElementById("message").style.display = "block";
            gsap.fromTo("#message", { scale: 0 }, { scale: 1, duration: 1, ease: "elastic.out(1, 0.5)" });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>


Hereâ€™s your interactive birthday adventure animation!

Click the cake â†’ It floats away.

Click the balloons â†’ They lift off.

Click the gift box â†’ A Happy Birthday message appears!


You can host this on a website or share it as a fun interactive greeting. Let me know if you need modifications!

